16	Q. With	respect	to	Exhibit	48,	sir,	do	you	recall
17	 having	a	conversation	with	J.D.	Oder	regarding	
18	 the	text	message	exchange	contained	in	Exhibit	48?
19	A. Yes.
20	 Q. And	what	do	you	recall	about	that	conversation?
21	 A. I	asked	him	whether	this	text	exchange	was	a	joke
22	 or	whether	he	had	any	indication	that	Mr.	Isaacman	
23	 believed	he	literally	was	in	the	Illuminati.
24	Q. What	did	Mr.	Oder	say?
25		A.	He	said	it	was	a	joke.
